      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Ready for your next adventure? This vehicle is in wonderful, reliable condition and has been lovingly maintained to ensure it's ready for the road. It offers a smooth ride, a clean interior, and the dependable performance you need in a daily driver. It\u2019s a fantastic, solid choice for anyone looking for quality and value!",
