    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some minor dings, and the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and dashboard. Mechanically, it is sound and runs well, but it is not in showroom condition. It is a practical choice for someone looking for a dependable car at an affordable price point.",
